      "earlyWarningSignal": "Within 30 days: observe whether SFP/SFJ acquirer management attempts to monetise NF/SFP's creative output through commercial channels that NF/SFP did not previously use. Forced commercial application of creative work is the SFP/SFJ extraction mechanism operating on NF/SFP's primary resource.",
